Class OrderedListSet<E>

java.lang.Object
  set.OrderedListSet<E>
Type Parameters:
E - the set type.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Set<E>
public class OrderedListSet<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Set<E>

The OrderedListSet is a set that further guarantees that its elements are in ascending element order, sorted according to the natural ordering of its elements ( DefaultComparator ), or by a Comparator provided at OrderedListSet creation time. Several additional operations are provided to take advantage of the ordering.

1.0
